peregrine
Class StructReaders

java.lang.Object
  peregrine.StructReaders

public class StructReaders
extends java.lang.Object

Create a StructReader around primitive types, varints, hashcodes, etc.

Variable length struct readers can be joined by calling splice and unsplice. Fixed width struct readers can be combined into a new StructReader by calling join and unjoin.

splice

public static StructReader splice(java.util.List<StructReader> list)
Wrap a list of StructReader so that we can have a new struct which has each StructReader in this list prefixed with a varint so we can unpack it with StructReader.readSlice(). One can call unwrap to get the original list.
